
Problem statement
=================
-composed of:
 1. context (of the problem)
 2. problem
 3. forces (influence solution choice)
 4. solution (balances forces)
 5. consequences (of chosen solution)
-get high-level (business) use case of software implementation (based on problem)
 :note: use case == actor, system, system-actor value

OOD Steps:
==========
:goal: establish areas of responsibility
:note: methodology provided for some perspective on how to break work into manageable pieces
1. summarize approach to solution
2. describe overall strategy to follow
3. describe technical foundations (of software solution)
4. specfic/technical considerations that define approach's common aspects

